1.disclaimer: Available to the first Starbucks Odyssey members who select this Benefit by April 30, 2023. You will receive access for you and a guest to a personalized event ("Event") at your choice of either the Seattle, New York, or Chicago participating Starbucks Reserve store locations. Transportation and lodging not included. Once selected your Event time and date cannot be rescheduled. Event access is not transferable and not valid for resale.. Event substitution or transfer are not permitted. Starbucks reserves the right to substitute an Event (or portion thereof) at its sole discretion in the event of unforeseen circumstances beyond its reasonable control.

active.intro: Welcome to our First-Ever Benefit Selection Period

1.body: Until April 30th, you can choose one Benefit if you've unlocked any Levels.
1.headline: Choose Your Favorite

2.body: Remember: Some Benefits are limited quantity so select your favorite while they last.

1.body: You'll decide the name of a coffee tree at our first coffee farm, Hacienda Alsacia, located in beautiful Costa Rica. Dedicate the tree to your best friend, your dog, or even yourself — the possibilities are endless.

freeCoffeeForAMonth.headline: 30 Days of Free Drinks

1.disclaimer:
Items redeemed per this Benefit do not count toward completion of a Starbucks Odyssey Journey activity.

Between 5/11 and 6/9, members who select this benefit can enjoy a free Starbucks beverage ($10 limit) once a day at a participating store by using the coupon in their Starbucks Rewards account. These coupons are valid for all handcrafted beverages, excluding alcohol and canned or bottled beverages. A coupon not used on any given day does not carry over to the next day.
1.headline:
30 Days of
Free Drinks
1.body: Free Starbucks drinks, anyone? Every day for 30 days, you'll receive a coupon in your Starbucks app that can be redeemed for one free beverage up to $10.

2.body: By clicking below, you are confirming your selection of 30 Days of Free Drinks. Confirming is final and cannot be undone.
2.headline: Confirm Your Selection

freeCoffeeForAMonth.body: Get one of your favorite beverages every day for 30 days, on us.

liveTastingEvent.body: Attend a virtual coffee tasting paired with a bag of coffee.

1.body: Receive a coupon for a bag of Starbucks coffee beans, pick it up in-store, and enjoy a virtual tasting hosted live by our partners in Costa Rica.
1.headline: Virtual Tasting and Coffee

2.body: Learn how to taste our coffee like a pro! Select one of the live events below.
2.headline: Book Your Virtual Tasting

3.disclaimer:
Tasting time and date is subject to availability and may not be rescheduled. The Virtual Coffee Tasting event is exclusive to you; content cannot be downloaded, recorded or shared externally.

Free bag of coffee redeemed as a coupon automatically loaded to your Starbucks® Rewards account. Coupon valid from 4/24/2023 -5/31/2023 at participating stores. Max coupon value $16.00 (you are responsible for any costs exceeding this amount). No cash redemption value.
3.headline: Confirm Your Selection
